      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 352,
        "height": 704,
        "content": "# üöÄ SaaS Onboarding Drip\nThis workflow automates a 5-step email sequence for new users stored in Notion. It handles welcome emails, pro-tips, check-ins, and trial expiration alerts automatically.\n\n## How it works\n1. **Checks Database:** Runs daily to find users matching specific criteria (e.g., \"Registered 3 days ago\").\n2. **Sends Emails:** Uses Gmail to send the relevant email for that stage.\n3. **Updates CRM:** Marks the stage as \"Completed\" in Notion to prevent duplicate sends.\n4. **Alerts Team:** Sends a Telegram notification if a lead is unresponsive after 7 days.\n\n## Setup steps\n1. **Configure Nodes:** Open the `üìù CONFIGURATION` node to set your email subjects, body text, and Telegram Chat ID.\n2. **Connect Accounts:** Add your credentials for Notion, Gmail, and Telegram.\n3. **Map Database:** In the Notion nodes, select your specific database and ensure property names match."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
